ssful program at a large research institution, the authors provide a practical manual, complete with examples, forms, and templates that cover all aspects of establishing and maintaining a loanable technology program.  a29 43 0aLibrary circulation and loans. 0aMultimedia library services. 0aLibrariesxSpecial collectionsxAudio-visual equipment. 0aLibrariesxSpecial collectionsxNonbook materials.1 aMestre, Lori,eauthor.1 aKurt, Eric.,d1979-eauthor. 0aPractical guides for librarians ;vno. 13.  aZ712 .S36 2015hGMCT-OS-Bi1007558750p77.11kAVAIL_SOON  a888555839  aZ712 .S36 2015wLCc1i1007558750d5/8/2015lON_SHELFmGR_MACEWANp$77.11rYsYtBOOKu4/27/2015  aZ 712 S36 2015wLCc1i0162035299203lON_SHELFmUAHSSp$150.00rYsYtBOOKu5/27/2015zCOUTTS_ADD01bhttp://viaf.org/viaf/311770029